              <h1 style="color: #3D5161;margin-top: 0px;font-family: Tahoma;">Marketing</h1>
              <p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">The marketing team delivered a digital first promotion for Slimming World offering readers the chance to join free of charge using high-impact editorial and advertising formats: articles, newsletters, webstrips, digital display and social media across all NI & ROI sites. This was complemented by pre-promo ads in print, an 8-page recipe pullout in the Irish Daily Mirror & Mirror NI, and two magazines in the Irish Daily Star, Irish Daily Mirror & Mirror NI. We have seen exceptional results across the board.                                                                       Adam visiting baby Adam for the first time! Thanks Maggie for sharing these adorable photos!
</p>
