          <div id="Commercial">
            <div id="myHeader" style="background-color: #fed780;padding: 20px;margin: 10px;">
              <h1 style="color: #3D5161;margin-top: 0px;font-family: Tahoma;">Commercial</h1>
              <p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">Our commercial teams have been busy with a brilliant start to 2023 with big wins and media partnerships such as Beauty Excellence from our NI team whilst the Dublin office has had some great wins from Nicorette, Sensodyne, and Boyle Sports. On top of this, we’ve had a team restructure with Hugh Crowther appointed as Group Sales Director for Reach Solutions in ROI. Hugh now heads up the entire commercial function in the market, continuing our transformation to a digital-first business. When he’s not working, Hugh can be found practising his other passions - darts and debating a juicy conspiracy theory.  Wishing Hugh the very best of luck in his new role. 
Also a big welcome to Tess Braidner who has joined the commercial team as an intern for 15 weeks from the University of Belfast.</p>

