              <p style="color: #3D5161;font-family: Tahoma;">It is essential Fire & Security requirements that everyone signs in & out of the Belfast office Hub. There is a book as you enter that needs to be filled in on arrival and when leaving the office (even for lunch/meetings etc). This is an official document for Health & Safety or a Fire emergency. Thank you for your cooperation. 
